    <metadata>
        <name>Alpine panoramic trail: Schwarzsee-Jaun</name>
        <desc>Most of this stage runs along natural footpaths and almost all of it lies within the village of Jaun. It links Schwarzsee to Jaun via the Brecca valley, an exceptional glacial feature, with a fascinating karstic landscape that is home to some very special fauna and flora. The Euschelspassseparates the two valleys. Take the opportunity to discover the Gastlosen mountain chain, with its impressive limestone cliffs, before dropping down to the village of Jaun, with its well-preserved heritage.</desc>
        <time>2026-04-26T15:56:42+02:00</time>
            </metadata>
